{"url": "https://people.com/royals/prince-harry-asking-prince-charles-to-walk-meghan-markle-down-aisle-wedding/", "text": "Prince Harry is opening up about the poignant moment he asked his dad to walk Meghan Markle down the aisle at their royal wedding in May.\n\nHarry, 34, approached Prince Charles, who celebrates his 70th birthday next week, to step in after Meghan\u2019s father, Thomas Markle, was unable to come to the Windsor Castle nuptials.\n\nIn the documentary, Prince, Son and Heir: Charles at 70, which airs on BBC One on Thursday, Harry says: \u201cI asked him to and I think he knew it was coming and he immediately said, \u2018Yes, of course, I\u2019ll do whatever Meghan needs and I\u2019m here to support you.\u2019 \u201d\n\n\u201cFor him that\u2019s a fantastic opportunity to step up and be that support, and you know he\u2019s our father so of course he\u2019s gonna be there for us.\u201d\n\nREX/Shutterstock\n\nAs Charles led Meghan to Harry\u2019s side during the historic ceremony at St. George\u2019s Chapel, the prince turned to his dad and said, \u201cThank you, Pa.\u201d\n\nCharles\u2019 wife, Camilla, Duchess of Cornwall, couldn\u2019t see what was said between son and his father at the altar, but says she watched it later on TV.\n\n\u201cI think that was very touching, sitting where I was, you couldn\u2019t hear what he said. But afterwards watching it on the television, I\u2026 I think it was a very\u2026 it was a lovely gesture,\u201d she says.\n\nOf the emotional moment, Harry adds: \u201cYou\u2019ve gotta say thank you. Just because he\u2019s my father that doesn\u2019t mean I can just sort of go, \u2018Okay, that\u2019s all, I\u2019ll take it from here.\u2019 \u201d\n\nThen he quips, \u201cErr, no, that is what I wanted to say but erm\u2026and I was very grateful for him to be able to do that.\u201d\n\nPrince Charles and Camilla, Duchess of Cornwall, at Meghan Markle and Prince Harry\u2019s May wedding. Jonathan Brady - WPA Pool/Getty Images\n\nAs for the moment when Charles took Meghan\u2019s mom, Doria Ragland, by the arm to head into a private room to sign the marriage register, Camilla says: \u201cA lot of people, seeing my husband actually take the bride\u2019s mother by the hand to sign the registry, it\u2019s something that moved everybody.\n\n\u201cIt\u2019s the things he does behind the scenes that people don\u2019t know about. I don\u2019t think people realize quite how kind he is.\u201d", "images": ["https://people.com/thmb/ZvAhd1PP9kO8x1nmx6CeYcy_3YA=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Queen-Elizabeth-Prince-Philip-wedding-1-jpg-cbe332a4d2d0478eb4d1827f590aa3a4.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/EKlxP0gNpam0YcjHBNxV0IkpMUQ=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/prince-harry-serena-williams-meghan-markle-baby2baby-gala-west-hollywood-111025-d2d224a5d9a445b9839798ef38914e9d.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/k2MVcpPRLlF0coL7S6yFEwfocMw=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/prince-harry-meghan-markle-110725-bdaa13e8ec84464a88ae53b8344cbde0.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/26_J2fAXIKk0V705Qyb0Cs44ois=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/meghan-markle-prince-harry-1-111325-07ba1342d900451385e988735fb1cf84.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/9TERAv8bYCbf1qQ2iJkGfxUWd5Q=/200x200/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/IMG_8390-366ad20f0fe844fead1082b6ad77d1a4.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/ovFNjWLrSqBrPgcwAplysMT2Dak=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Meghan-Markle-attends-Fortune-Most-Powerful-Women-Summit-2025-meghan-markle-archie-lilibet-111825-77fa47a901cd40ff9ccc169af46c5fd9.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/xO7Cxp7EAV874Xo6cW9cgrCgJN4=/4000x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(999x0:1001x2)/charles-camilla-1-2000-59fcb589a756402490c98e107ed43c1a.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/Uo8iLTyanrj7eNHYmSXZHwHJbxY=/800x533/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Spen